            . On the 14th of September, the prisoner brought to our warehouse a written order, signed Weatherhall and Co. (who deal with us), which I produce - it is for four dozen of common and four dozen of best crown mixed pins. I told him we had no common pins; he said he would take the best - I delivered four dozen to him, and he took them away; he had been to the house before. In the course of the day he came, and said he would have four dozen more of the best, which I delivered him with the invoice. The goods were delivered on the faith of this order.</p>
